snippets.title: CacheService updateCachedContent Sample
snippets.description: Updates CachedContent resource (only expiration is updatable).

snippets.title: CacheService generateMessage Sample
snippets.description: Generates a response from the model given an input `MessagePrompt`.

snippets.title: CacheService countMessageTokens Sample
snippets.description: Runs a model's tokenizer on a string and returns the token count.

snippets.title: CacheService listFiles Sample
snippets.description: Lists the metadata for `File`s owned by the requesting project.

snippets.title: CacheService getFile Sample
snippets.description: Gets the metadata for the given `File`.

snippets.title: CacheService generateContent Sample
snippets.description: Generates a model response given an input `GenerateContentRequest`. Refer to the [text generation guide](https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/text-generation) for detailed usage information. Input capabilities differ between models, including tuned models. Refer to the [model guide](https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/models/gemini) and [tuning guide](https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/model-tuning) for details.

snippets.title: CacheService generateAnswer Sample
snippets.description: Generates a grounded answer from the model given an input `GenerateAnswerRequest`.

snippets.title: CacheService streamGenerateContent Sample
snippets.description: Generates a [streamed response](https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/text-generation?lang=python#generate-a-text-stream) from the model given an input `GenerateContentRequest`.

snippets.title: CacheService embedContent Sample
snippets.description: Generates a text embedding vector from the input `Content` using the specified [Gemini Embedding model](https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/models/gemini#text-embedding).

snippets.title: CacheService batchEmbedContents Sample
snippets.description: Generates multiple embedding vectors from the input `Content` which consists of a batch of strings represented as `EmbedContentRequest` objects.

snippets.title: CacheService countTokens Sample
snippets.description: Runs a model's tokenizer on input `Content` and returns the token count. Refer to the [tokens guide](https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/tokens) to learn more about tokens.

snippets.title: CacheService bidiGenerateContent Sample
snippets.description: Low-Latency bidirectional streaming API that supports audio and video streaming inputs can produce multimodal output streams (audio and text).

snippets.title: CacheService getModel Sample
snippets.description: Gets information about a specific `Model` such as its version number, token limits, [parameters](https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/models/generative-models#model-parameters) and other metadata. Refer to the [Gemini models guide](https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/models/gemini) for detailed model information.

snippets.title: CacheService listModels Sample
snippets.description: Lists the [`Model`s](https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/models/gemini) available through the Gemini API.

snippets.title: CacheService getTunedModel Sample
snippets.description: Gets information about a specific TunedModel.

snippets.title: CacheService createTunedModel Sample
snippets.description: Creates a tuned model. Check intermediate tuning progress (if any) through the [google.longrunning.Operations] service. Access status and results through the Operations service. Example:   GET /v1/tunedModels/az2mb0bpw6i/operations/000-111-222

snippets.title: CacheService createPermission Sample
snippets.description: Create a permission to a specific resource.

snippets.title: CacheService getPermission Sample
snippets.description: Gets information about a specific Permission.

snippets.title: CacheService listPermissions Sample
snippets.description: Lists permissions for the specific resource.

snippets.title: CacheService transferOwnership Sample
snippets.description: Transfers ownership of the tuned model. This is the only way to change ownership of the tuned model. The current owner will be downgraded to writer role.

snippets.title: CacheService listCorpora Sample
snippets.description: Lists all `Corpora` owned by the user.

snippets.title: CacheService generateText Sample
snippets.description: Generates a response from the model given an input message.

snippets.title: CacheService embedText Sample
snippets.description: Generates an embedding from the model given an input message.

snippets.title: CacheService batchEmbedText Sample
snippets.description: Generates multiple embeddings from the model given input text in a synchronous call.

snippets.title: CacheService countTextTokens Sample
snippets.description: Runs a model's tokenizer on a text and returns the token count.
